In [63]:

In [65]:
cheap_reviews_text = ' '.join(cheap_wines['description'].dropna())
exp_reviews_text = ' '.join(exp_wines['description'].dropna())
In [57]:

Out[60]:

In [66]:
from nltk.tokenize import word_tokenize
from nltk.corpus import stopwords
from nltk import FreqDist
stop_words = set(stopwords.words('english'))
cheap_tokens = [word.lower() for word in word_tokenize(cheap_reviews_text) if word.isalpha() and word.lower() not in stop_words]
exp_tokens = [word.lower() for word in word_tokenize(exp_reviews_text) if word.isalpha() and word.lower() not in stop_words]
In [67]:
cheap_word_freq = FreqDist(cheap_tokens)
exp_word_freq = FreqDist(exp_tokens)
In [68]:
cheap_pmi = {word: cheap_word_freq[word] / exp_word_freq[word] for word in cheap_word_freq if word in exp_word_freq}
In [69]:
cheap_wordcloud = WordCloud(width=800, height=400, background_color='white').generate_from_frequencies(cheap_word_freq)
exp_wordcloud = WordCloud(width=800, height=400, background_color='white').generate_from_frequencies(exp_word_freq)
